node.text:
With the stressful pandemic and ongoing travel restrictions keeping us at home, I think we could all use a little bit more fun right now! Wake up your imagination & escape with me on a worry free ride through the entertainment capital of the world! 🍹🎭🥃🎢⛲️🥂🦈

I know that Las Vegas is hurting badly and since I had never shared all of this work together before, I decided to create a long format edit from my 2018 campaign for @MGMResortsintl. Big thanks to @TylerFairbank & @TommyLundberg for helping me bring these time-consuming animations to life. Make sure to turn your phone sideways and watch the full screen version! 🔊🙌🏻

Let me know your favorite part in the comments!
.
.
.
.
.

node.text:
Misty moods up in Bend, Oregon ✨
I’ll never forget this sunrise mission with a bunch of photographer friends. We woke up while it was still dark out and made it to this picture perfect lake surrounded by wild flowers just in time to see the colors come to life. That dreamy mist was like the cherry on top! 😍
(Ad) 📸 Pictures captured on my high speed @KingstonTechnology 256 GB Canvas React Plus memory card. #KingstonIsWithYou
.

.

Symmetry & Shapes in Shenzhen 🇨🇳

Orange skies over the California coast ✨
This was one of those special nights with friends where I didn’t have my nice Sony camera with me and wasn’t planning on taking any photos. After a peaceful sunset walk through the Palisades, we ended up at this lookout spot along the bluffs with views all the way down the coast that I had never seen before. As the sky lit up with color, I pulled out my trusty iPhone and tried to capture it the best I could. Nothing groundbreaking, but these are the magic moments that make me love living here so much. 🧡
.
.
.
.
.
